We will expand the size of the waitlist in the meantime so that students can at least get on the waitlist using their phase 2.

I will still try to get in waiting list on Monday Morning when my phase 2 begins, and see if there's anyone who drop of the 350/350 waiting list. I will also talk to the advisor to see if there's anything else I can do. I really need this class for next semester.
